'''吉第安·阿德龙'''（{{lang-en|Gideon Adlon}}；{{bd|1997年|3月30日|||catIdx=Gideon Adlon}}）是一位美國女演員。

==生平==
1997年3月30日，吉第安·阿德龙出生在[[美国|美国]]，母亲是女演员[[帕梅拉·阿德龙|帕梅拉·阿德龙]]。父亲费利克斯·O·阿德隆拥有美国和[[德国|德国]]双重国籍。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://dujour.com/news/gideon-adlon-blockers-travel-guide-los-angeles/|title=Gideon Adlon's Guide to Los Angeles|journal=Du Jour|first=Samuel|last=Anderson|accessdate=2021-02-01|archive-date=2018-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180607002349/http://dujour.com/news/gideon-adlon-blockers-travel-guide-los-angeles/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tvovermind.com/gideon-adlon/|title=10 Things You Didn’t Know About Gideon Adlon|journal=TVOvermind|first=Liz|last=Flynn|accessdate=2021-02-01|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803151039/https://www.tvovermind.com/gideon-adlon/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="thecut">{{cite web|last1=Silman|first1=Anna|title=Pamela Adlon's Daughter Gideon Is Ready for Anything|url=https://www.thecut.com/2018/04/pamela-adlons-daughter-gideon-is-ready-for-anything.html|publisher=New York|accessdate=2021-02-01|date=2018-04-06|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109031142/https://www.thecut.com/2018/04/pamela-adlons-daughter-gideon-is-ready-for-anything.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>她的妹妹{{Link-en|敖德萨·阿德隆|Odessa A'zion}}也是女演员。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Friedlander|first1=Whitney|title=Pamela Adlon makes perfect roast chicken. But she’s not trying to be a jerk about it|url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/tv/story/2020-03-04/pamela-adlon-better-things-fx-cooking|publisher=[[New_York_(magazine)|New York]]|accessdate=September 17, 2020|date=March 4, 2020|archive-date=2021-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216181644/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/tv/story/2020-03-04/pamela-adlon-better-things-fx-cooking|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她的祖父{{Link-en|柏西·艾德隆|Percy Adlon}}是德国电影制作人。她的外祖父是[[美国犹太人|美国犹太人]]作家、制片人唐·塞格尔。<ref>{{cite web|title=Gideon Adlon chats about her first major role in Blockers|url=https://www.tribute.ca/news/gideon-adlon-chats-about-her-first-major-role-in-blockers/2018/07/05/|publisher=Tribute|accessdate=2021-02-01|date=2018-07-05|archive-date=2021-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206004146/https://www.tribute.ca/news/gideon-adlon-chats-about-her-first-major-role-in-blockers/2018/07/05/|dead-url=no}}</ref>她的外祖母是[[英格兰|英格兰]][[圣公会|圣公会]]教徒。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://jewishjournal.com/culture/arts/311181/art-reflects-life-in-pamela-adlons-better-things/|title=Pamela Adlon Wants You to Know ‘Better Things’ is Scripted|accessdate=2021-02-01|date=2020-02-27|website=Jewish Journal|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129031717/https://jewishjournal.com/culture/arts/311181/art-reflects-life-in-pamela-adlons-better-things/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

